title: Users are not allowed to use pseudonyms, as trust and transparency between users regarding their identities is relevant to the service.
quoteText: Some features, such as the ability to send money to another Cash App user with the balance in your Account, may be available only if you provide us with certain information about you and we are able to verify your identity.
